ultiplets but unstable in amplitudes and/or frequencies. The\ndensity of periodicities also make KIC 10139564 challenging to explain using\npublished models. This menagerie of properties should provide tight constraints\non structural models, making this subdwarf B star the most promising for\napplying asteroseismology.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Jun 2012 07:09:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
